regen.absent_element: procedure for reestablishing call if it fails in any cab other than the lead
regen.new_specification: If the call fails in any cab other than the lead, the driver in that cab shall call the lead cab to request reestablishment of the call.

regen.absent_element: situation where a driver in another cab requests call reestablishment upon failure
regen.new_specification: If the call fails in a cab other than the lead traction vehicle, the driver in that cab shall initiate a request to the lead driver for call reestablishment.

regen.absent_element: The procedure when a call fails in any cab other than the lead cab
regen.new_specification: If the call fails in any cab other than the lead cab, the driver in that cab shall be responsible for calling the lead cab and requesting reestablishment of the call.

label: If the call fails to any other cab, the driver in that cab will call the lead cab and request re-establishment of the call.
absence: situation of call failure in other cabs(not the lead traction vehicle)
